      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "CHANGING THE DEFAULT PROFILE"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "Anytime a new profile is created, its configurations is brought"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "over from the DEFAULT profile.  The DEFAULT profile is just like"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "any other, and may be modified in a similar fashion."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "To change the DEFAULT profile values, go to Panel 0.7, and select"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "the DEFAULT profile from the selection list that is displayed with"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "the 'S' line command.  The subsequent Profile Definition panels"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "will display the values of the current DEFAULT profile, and"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "may be changed as desired."
      },
